'''''Non nobis solum''''' ([[Latin language|Latin]] "Not for ourselves alone") is the motto of [[Burnie]], in [[Tasmania]], [[Australia]]. It appeared on the council seal of the town until 1992, when the seal was updated to a new, more colourful one without the motto present. 

It is also the motto of [[Lower Canada College]], a private school in Quebec, and the [[Massanutten Military Academy]] in Virginia.


